WEBVTT

00:02:29.772 --> 00:02:32.503
Evolyutsiya jarayonida 
imildoqlarning 1100 dan ortiq turi

00:02:32.503 --> 00:02:36.322
paydo bo'ldi. Ularning bizga 
ma'lum bo'lmagan

00:02:36.322 --> 00:02:39.653
yana ko'plab turlari 
bo'lsa ajab emas.

00:02:39.653 --> 00:02:44.783
Imildoqlar juda chidamli bo'lgani uchun 
deyarli hamma yerda uchraydi.

00:02:44.783 --> 00:02:48.463
Ular barcha qit'ada, shu jumladan, 
Antarktidada ham hayot kechiradi.

00:02:48.463 --> 00:02:51.152
Ularni turli xil ekotizimlarda, 
masalan, cho'llarda,

00:02:51.152 --> 00:02:52.283
muzliklarda,

00:02:52.283 --> 00:02:53.182
dengizda,

00:02:53.182 --> 00:02:54.143
chuchuk suvda,

00:02:54.143 --> 00:02:55.233
o'rmonlarda va

00:02:55.233 --> 00:02:57.242
tog' cho'qqilarida uchratish mumkin.

00:02:57.242 --> 00:03:00.913
Imildoqlarni bog', park 
va o'rmonlarda uchrovchi mox va